---

<section class="bg-white px-4 py-24 dark:bg-brand-dark">
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <div class="mx-auto mb-16 max-w-3xl text-center">
      <h2
        class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white md:text-4xl"
      >
        Kennen Sie dieses <span class="text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-500"
          >Chaos</span
        >?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        Trotz modernster Tools fühlen sich viele Prozesse an wie Arbeit am
        Fließband, nur ohne das Fließband.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-24 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div
        class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-lg shadow-orange-500/5 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5 dark:shadow-none"
      >
        <div class="mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div
            class="flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-orange-50 text-orange-600 dark:bg-orange-500/10 dark:text-orange-400"
          >
            <svg
              class="h-8 w-8"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M8 7v8a2 2 0 002 2h6M8 7V5a2 2 0 012-2h4.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l4.414 4.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V15a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2M8 7H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2v-2"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3
          class="mb-3 text-center text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
        >
          Copy-Paste Wahnsinn
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-center text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400"
        >
          Daten werden manuell von E-Mails in Excel und dann ins ERP kopiert.
          Fehler sind vorprogrammiert.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-lg shadow-orange-500/5 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5 dark:shadow-none"
      >
        <div class="mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div
            class="flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-orange-50 text-orange-600 dark:bg-orange-500/10 dark:text-orange-400"
          >
            <svg
              class="h-8 w-8"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3
          class="mb-3 text-center text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
        >
          Zeitfresser Reporting
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-center text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400"
        >
          Jeden Montag werden Stunden damit verschwendet, Zahlen aus drei
          Systemen zusammenzusuchen.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-lg shadow-orange-500/5 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5 dark:shadow-none"
      >
        <div class="mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div
            class="flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-orange-50 text-orange-600 dark:bg-orange-500/10 dark:text-orange-400"
          >
            <svg
              class="h-8 w-8"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728A9 9 0 015.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3
          class="mb-3 text-center text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
        >
          Kopfmonopole
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-center text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400"
        >
          "Das weiß nur die Petra." Wenn eine Person ausfällt, steht plötzlich
          der ganze Prozess still.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-orange-50/50 p-8 dark:border-white/10 dark:bg-white/5 md:p-12"
    >
      <div class="mb-12 text-center">
        <h3 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
          Warum zögern Sie noch?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Lassen Sie uns mit den drei größten Mythen aufräumen.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div
          class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm dark:bg-white/5 dark:border dark:border-white/10 dark:shadow-none"
        >
          <div
            class="mb-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500"
          >
            Mythos
          </div>
          <p
            class="mb-6 min-h-14 text-lg font-medium italic text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
          >
            "Automatisierung lohnt sich nur für große Konzerne."
          </p>
          <div class="mb-6 h-px w-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-white/10"></div>
          <div
            class="mb-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-500"
          >
            Realität
          </div>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Gerade KMUs profitieren sofort. Tools wie n8n machen es heute
            wirtschaftlich, in Tagen, nicht Monaten.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm dark:bg-white/5 dark:border dark:border-white/10 dark:shadow-none"
        >
          <div
            class="mb-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500"
          >
            Mythos
          </div>
          <p
            class="mb-6 min-h-14 text-lg font-medium italic text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
          >
            "Das dauert ewig und kostet ein Vermögen."
          </p>
          <div class="mb-6 h-px w-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-white/10"></div>
          <div
            class="mb-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-500"
          >
            Realität
          </div>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Ein klar abgegrenzter Prozess ist in
            <span class="font-bold text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-500"
              >48 Stunden</span
            >
            produktiv und spart ab Tag 3 Geld.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-8 shadow-sm dark:bg-white/5 dark:border dark:border-white/10 dark:shadow-none"
        >
          <div
            class="mb-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500"
          >
            Mythos
          </div>
          <p
            class="mb-6 min-h-14 text-lg font-medium italic text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
          >
            "Unsere Abläufe sind viel zu individuell."
          </p>
          <div class="mb-6 h-px w-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-white/10"></div>
          <div
            class="mb-3 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-500"
          >
            Realität
          </div>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            Genau dafür baue ich
            <span class="font-bold text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-500"
              >individuelle Workflows</span
            >, die sich Ihrem Prozess anpassen, nicht umgekehrt.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
